msgstr "Huidig helderheidsniveau."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "The current brightness level."
msgstr "Het huidige helderheidsniveau."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "Mouse cursor brightness control."
msgstr "Helderheidsregeling muiscursor."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid ""
"When enabled, the mouse cursor follows the brightness setting. When "
"disabled, the mouse cursor always remains at full brightness. Controlling "
"mouse cursor brightness can sometimes show the wrong cursor and introduce "
"cursor lag, and may prevent the display from sleeping (the software cursor "
"loop keeps the screen active). Disable it if you encounter cursor issues or "
"if your computer stops sleeping. Note that when other Gnome Shell components "
"clone the mouse (like the Zoom accessibility feature), this feature may not "
"work correctly, or there may be multiple cursors shown on the screen."
msgstr ""


#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "Keyboard shortcut: increase brightness."
msgstr "Sneltoets: helderheid verhogen."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "Keyboard shortcut to increase the brightness by one step (5%). Set to an empty list to disable."
msgstr "Sneltoets om de helderheid met één stap (5%) te verhogen. Stel in op een lege lijst om uit te schakelen."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "Keyboard shortcut: decrease brightness."
msgstr "Sneltoets: helderheid verlagen."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "Keyboard shortcut to decrease the brightness by one step (5%). Set to an empty list to disable."
msgstr "Sneltoets om de helderheid met één stap (5%) te verlagen. Stel in op een lege lijst om uit te schakelen."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "Debugging."
msgstr "Foutopsporing."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "Enable debugging for the extension."
msgstr "Schakel foutopsporing in voor de extensie."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "Gamma curve exponent."
msgstr "Gammacoëfficiënt."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid ""
"Controls the gamma curve used for dimming. A value of 1.0 is linear. "
"Values above 1.0 preserve shadows better while compressing highlights more "
"aggressively — 2.0 is the recommended starting point."
msgstr ""
"Bepaalt de gammacurve voor verduistering. Een waarde van 1,0 is lineair. "
"Waarden boven 1,0 bewaren donkere gebieden beter terwijl lichte gebieden "
"sterker worden gecomprimeerd — 2,0 is het aanbevolen startpunt."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid "Per-workspace brightness memory."
msgstr "Helderheidsgeheugen per werkruimte."

#: schemas/org.gnome.shell.extensions.soft-brightness-plus.gschema.xml
msgid ""
"When enabled, the extension remembers a separate brightness level for each "
"workspace and restores it automatically when you switch. Set brightness on "
"each workspace once; switching will apply that workspace's saved level "
"thereafter."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer ingeschakeld onthoudt de extensie een apart helderheidsniveau voor "
"elke werkruimte en herstelt dit automatisch bij het wisselen. Stel de "
"helderheid eenmalig in per werkruimte; bij het wisselen wordt het opgeslagen "
"niveau toegepast."
